{"expand": "renderedFields,names,schema,operations,editmeta,changelog,versionedRepresentations", "id": "13619654", "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/13619654", "key": "HADOOP-19582", "fields": {"summary": "Backport HADOOP-15984 (Update jersey from 1.19 to 2.x) on branch-3.4.0 ", "description": "In Hadoop 3.5.0 we uses GlassFish Jersey (modern Jersey).\r\n\r\nIn Hadoop 3.4.0 we use Sun Jersey (legacy Jersey).\r\n\r\nJetty submodule is not published under _com.sun.jersey.jersey-test-framework_ so upgrading jersey will be a better idea to remove grizzly-http-* dependencies (which is already done in 3.5.0 through\u00a0 YARN-11793).\u00a0", "reporter": {"self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=susheel_7", "name": "susheel_7", "key": "JIRAUSER299573", "avatarUrls": {"48x48": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=34058", "24x24": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=34058", "16x16": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=34058", "32x32": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=34058"}, "displayName": "Susheel Gupta", "active": true, "timeZone": "Etc/UTC"}, "comment": {"comments": [{"self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/13619654/comment/17955184", "id": "17955184", "author": {"self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=slfan1989", "name": "slfan1989", "key": "slfan1989", "avatarUrls": {"48x48": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?ownerId=slfan1989&avatarId=40935", "24x24": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&ownerId=slfan1989&avatarId=40935", "16x16": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&ownerId=slfan1989&avatarId=40935", "32x32": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&ownerId=slfan1989&avatarId=40935"}, "displayName": "Shilun Fan", "active": true, "timeZone": "America/Vancouver"}, "body": "[~susheel_7]\u00a0Thank you for raising this JIRA. Regarding your suggestion, my current plan is not to upgrade Branch-3.4. The purpose of upgrading Jersey is to provide full support for JDK 17; however, Branch-3.4 is intended to continue supporting JDK 8, so we do not plan to apply this upgrade to that branch.\r\n\r\n\u00a0\r\n\r\ncc: [~hexiaoqiao]\u00a0[~stevel@apache.org]\u00a0", "updateAuthor": {"self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=slfan1989", "name": "slfan1989", "key": "slfan1989", "avatarUrls": {"48x48": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?ownerId=slfan1989&avatarId=40935", "24x24": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&ownerId=slfan1989&avatarId=40935", "16x16": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&ownerId=slfan1989&avatarId=40935", "32x32": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&ownerId=slfan1989&avatarId=40935"}, "displayName": "Shilun Fan", "active": true, "timeZone": "America/Vancouver"}, "created": "2025-05-30T11:10:32.310+0000", "updated": "2025-05-30T11:12:14.998+0000"}, {"self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/13619654/comment/17955185", "id": "17955185", "author": {"self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=fanningpj", "name": "fanningpj", "key": "fanningpj", "avatarUrls": {"48x48": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452", "24x24": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452", "16x16": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452", "32x32": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"}, "displayName": "PJ Fanning", "active": true, "timeZone": "Europe/Madrid"}, "body": "I agree that backporting this to 3.4 is problematic. I think this is much too large a change for a patch release.\r\nI think the priority should be on pushing for a 3.5.0 release.", "updateAuthor": {"self": "htt